openapi: 3.0.0
paths:
  /v3/openapi/image:
    post:
      requestBody:
        content:
          multipart/form-data:
            schema:
              properties:
                name:
                  type: string
                photo:
                  type: string
                  format: binary
            encoding:
              photo:
                contentType: image/jpeg, image/png
      responses:
        "200":
          description: OK
  /v3/openapi/headerString:
    post:
      requestBody:
        content:
          multipart/form-data:
            schema:
              properties:
                person:
                  type: object
                  properties:
                    name:
                      type: string
                    age:
                      type: number
            encoding:
              person:
                headers:
                  X-Custom-Header:
                    schema:
                      type: string
                    description: Sample String Header
      responses:
        "200":
          description: OK
  /v3/openapi/headerNumber:
    post:
      requestBody:
        content:
          multipart/form-data:
            schema:
              properties:
                person:
                  type: object
                  properties:
                    name:
                      type: string
                    age:
                      type: number
            encoding:
              person:
                headers:
                  X-Custom-Header:
                    schema:
                      type: number
                    description: Sample Number Header
      responses:
        "200":
          description: OK
  /v3/openapi/headerObject:
    post:
      requestBody:
        content:
          multipart/form-data:
            schema:
              properties:
                person:
                  type: object
                  properties:
                    name:
                      type: string
                    age:
                      type: number
            encoding:
              person:
                headers:
                  X-Custom-Header:
                    schema:
                      type: object
                      properties:
                        category:
                          type: string
                        height:
                          type: number
                        weight:
                          type: number 
                    description: Sample Object Header
      responses:
        "200":
          description: OK
  /v3/openapi/headerBoolean:
    post:
      requestBody:
        content:
          multipart/form-data:
            schema:
              properties:
                person:
                  type: object
                  properties:
                    name:
                      type: string
                    age:
                      type: number
            encoding:
              person:
                headers:
                  X-Custom-Header:
                    schema:
                      type: boolean                
                    description: Sample Boolean Header
      responses:
        "200":
          description: OK
  /v3/openapi/headerAll:
    post:
      requestBody:
        content:
          multipart/form-data:
            schema:
              properties:
                person:
                  type: object
                  properties:
                    name:
                      type: string
                    age:
                      type: number
            encoding:
              person:
                headers:
                  X-Custom-Header-One:
                    schema:
                      type: string
                    description: Sample String Header
                  X-Custom-Header-Two:
                    schema:
                      type: number
                    description: Sample Number Header
                  X-Custom-Header-Three:
                    schema:
                      type: object
                      properties:
                        name:
                          type: string
                        age:
                          type: number
                    description: Sample Object Header
                  X-Custom-Header-Four:
                    schema:
                      type: boolean
                    description: Sample Boolean Header
      responses:
        "200":
          description: OK
  /v3/openapi/imageAndHeaders:
    post:
      requestBody:
        content:
          multipart/form-data:
            schema:
              properties:
                name:
                  type: string
                photo:
                  type: string
                  format: binary
            encoding:
              photo:
                contentType: image/jpeg, image/png
                headers:
                  X-Custom-Header:
                    schema:
                      type: string
                    description: Sample Image and Custom Header  
      responses:
        "200":
          description: OK
